Coffee machine monitoring system.
Arduino based hardware & Java software, allows you to monitor your coffee machine via XMPP/google chat etc

Requirements:
    Maven 2
    RXTX java serial extention
    Arduino, a couple of resistors and 2 LDRs
    Some sort of wireless serial link (optional)
    
To build the java side of things, download the source and run:
    mvn assembly:assembly
    
If successful you should be able to run the jar file using:
    java -jar target/coffeeMonitor-0.0.1-SNAPSHOT-jar-with-dependencies.jar